.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
5 different pets are kept: cat, turtle, dog, ferret, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is between the fan of reggae and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the owner of the cat##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking    | singing  | skydiving | puzzles   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Pet   | turtle    | dog | ferret | chinchilla | cat   |

