 3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is the accountant##1
 5. the journalist is in the middle##1
 6. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the videographer is the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the prince-smoker is between the owner of the goldfish and the person driving the car##2
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person driving the car is the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the owner of the frog is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |     3      |       4       |     5     |
