 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the canadian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
11. the malaysian is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |      4      |      5      |
