 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of indie##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of salsa##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of soul##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Music-Genre       | soul | country | salsa  | indie | pop    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

